      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, a physical therapist sounds a bit much for just a twist. i'll just stick to the RICE method for like a week and see how it goes. if i just take 800mg of ibuprofen every 6 hours to deal with the pain, that should be fine right? i just really don't want to deal with doctors if i can just fix this myself at home.",
